data.description: This lovely traditional home is immaculate, inviting and spacious.  So CONVENIENT to Peachtree Industrial OR Buford Highway, shopping, restaurants and who doesn't LOVE all Sugar Hill and all it has to offer?!  As you enter this lovely home, the foyer with its gleaming hardwood floors is flanked by rooms on either side, living room on right can be used for separate living room/office/playroom etc. and then the room on the left, is your fabulous dining room leading into your beautiful kitchen, WHICH is complete with stainless steel appliances and granite countertops.  Enjoy the view from the breakfast area table overlooking the nature filled back yard!  The family room has the stairs going to the upstairs bedrooms/bathrooms all tucked away in the corner (so those are not the first thing you see inside the front door)!  The primary suite has the largest closet you will find in a home this size, GORGEOUS floors, an additional closet and TONS of light, check it OUT!  The other three bedrooms are spacious with newer carpeting. Do not forget to see the unfinished daylight basement, all yours for the finishing, including double doors and paver patio on one side for easy access for lawn equipment or roll up door.  And the pool/tennis in this community is VERY inviting and you won't want to miss!
